<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="59" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1226,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,345,1260,1284]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">Distribution.</emphasis>
New for 
<collectingCountry box="[444,517,1261,1284]" name="Ghana" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">Ghana</collectingCountry>
. Described and until now only known from the 
<typeStatus box="[1022,1068,1261,1284]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">type</typeStatus>
series collected in NE 
<collectingCountry name="Democratic Republic of the Congo" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">Democratic Republic of the Congo</collectingCountry>
(“Uele, Paulis”). The new data from 
<collectingCountry box="[789,858,1296,1319]" name="Ghana" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">Ghana</collectingCountry>
suggest that the species has a much wider distribution and is probably connected through a zone of tropical rain forests.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="59" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1226,1423]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,309,1364,1388]" pageId="5" pageNumber="59">Remarks.</emphasis>
